  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When initiative is rolled, mark 1 hostile creature. <br />A creature marked in this way, remains marked for the duration of this encounter or until killed. <br />An unconscious creature loses any marks. <br />Only one creature can be marked at a time. <br />While a creature is marked, add 1d4 to attack and damage rolls against the marked creature and suffer a 1d6 penalty to attack and damage rolls against creatures who are not marked.</p>",
